{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be secure and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Blue Spark Design</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #0056b3;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-left: 5px solid #0056b3;\n            background-color: #fdfdfd;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #004085;\n        }\n        .contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #003d80;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n            color: #fff;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .security-note {\n            font-size: 0.8em;\n            color: #666;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Blue Spark Design</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Web Design</h3>\n                <p>Creating visually appealing and user-friendly websites that drive results.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>\n                <p>Designing intuitive and engaging user interfaces and experiences.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Branding</h3>\n                <p>Developing strong brand identities that resonate with your target audience.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Blue Spark Design is a freelance agency dedicated to providing innovative and secure design solutions. We partner with businesses to bring their visions to life through expert web and brand design.</p>\n            <p class=\"security-note\">We prioritize the security of your data and implement best practices in all our digital solutions.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" required></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n            <p class=\"security-note\">Your message will be transmitted securely.</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Blue Spark Design. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}